	dprr:hasNoteText "Monetalis. In MRR 2.455, and Index, 633, delete the word B(arrus), and refer also to Crawford, RRC 1.266-267, no. 234, 137 B.C. Perhaps a son of T. Veturius Gracchi f. Sempronianus, augur from 174 (Badian, Arethusa 1, 1968, 31-36).\n" .
